<plot>This promotional film for the feature _Quick Before It Melts (1964)_ (qv) focuses on its smallest performer. In the movie, Milton Fox is a penguin that delivers mail at the Little America base on Antarctica. The penguin that will play Milton Fox was found at an animal farm in Southern California owned by 'John Moore (XVIII)' (qv), who has supplied many wild animals to movie studios over the years. After some training for the role he will play, Milton meets several of his human costars, including 'Robert Morse' (qv) and 'Yvonne Craig' (qv).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?370309</url></doc>
